    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏讨论群：763769813</strong></h2><br>新手入门以及一些常见问题（复制链接到浏览器查看）   <br><strong></strong><br><strong></strong><br><strong>再次感谢玩家SYX的支持</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这是一款很爽快！超耐玩！动作轻Rogue游戏！</strong></h2>2D像素、快节奏、双摇杆、随机迷宫、程序生成、超丰富Build战斗组合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/838424e8864c1bdaea27e41aa2f18b77.poster.avif?t=1744981718\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/838424e8864c1bdaea27e41aa2f18b77.webm?t=1744981718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/838424e8864c1bdaea27e41aa2f18b77.mp4?t=1744981718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>少年在异世界的车站醒来，没有任何记忆！<br>依稀记得内心那一丝含糊而坚定的渴望，登上轮回之塔，寻找自己命运的真相。<br>少年将踏入一个陌生而诡异的世界，神秘的旅人，隐藏的秘密。<br>然而，随着命运的轨迹逐步揭开……<br>屠龙少年，命握谁手？ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/62f787efa96c0bbe05ac23a37f29c09f.apng?t=1744981718\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/62f787efa96c0bbe05ac23a37f29c09f.poster.avif?t=1744981718\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=114 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>牺牲与成长！</strong></h2>在刀尖舔血的快节奏游戏体验中，选择牺牲自己的生命值来换取各种随机强化。<br>在战斗、死亡和重生的循环中，找到矛与盾的平衡，你是否能上命运轮回的塔顶?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>诅咒与增益！</strong></h2>走的路都算数！成长与诅咒，缘起缘灭！ <br>选择中庸和安全，还是敢于面对不确定性，直面自己的内心，做出只属于你的选择！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/2554168efa44960acf497228dae9d7a4.poster.avif?t=1744981718\" width=616 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/2554168efa44960acf497228dae9d7a4.webm?t=1744981718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> <br>无限挑战！在随机生成的随机迷宫关卡中，每一次重生、每一轮挑战都是全新的开始！<br>快节奏、双摇杆！无畏少年攀塔而上！战至终章！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/b43aa268777a8cb30d1042576d3f2c6c.poster.avif?t=1744981718\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/b43aa268777a8cb30d1042576d3f2c6c.webm?t=1744981718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/b43aa268777a8cb30d1042576d3f2c6c.mp4?t=1744981718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>超丰富的战斗Build组合！八种主手枪械性能各异、几十种副手武器一较长短！<br>数以千计，献祭、宝箱、遗宝、诅咒、神秘房间。<br>百万级的随机组合概率，每一次轮回注定不同！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/4bd365a3098015fceb6f50ceb0a9a27d.poster.avif?t=1744981718\" width=616 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/4bd365a3098015fceb6f50ceb0a9a27d.webm?t=1744981718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>失忆少年，迷途车站，轮回之塔。</strong></h2>- 解锁各种蓝图装修游戏中的“家”，愈加美观，更多功能。<br>- 命运逐渐展开，探索世界真相。慢慢在各个区域中探寻各类NPC，他们会给予少年命运的指引，亦会成为下一次战斗中随机出现的强大助力。<br>- 堕落之地，更强的敌人，更高的回报。<br>- 神秘房间，随机出现并提供神秘的奖励。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/ab8ab780884546cc9ea7cd0e8b515496.poster.avif?t=1744981718\" width=616 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175460/extras/ab8ab780884546cc9ea7cd0e8b515496.webm?t=1744981718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富、体贴的辅助功能选项</strong></h2>自动射击、辅助瞄准、区分敌我描边、更详细的屏显等。<br>根据自己的游戏水平各取所需，更好地掌握自己的命之轮回！",
